00:10:40.580 --> 00:10:44.340
So today we wanna talk
about FFmpeg and VLC.

00:10:45.340 --> 00:10:48.620
For context for people who
are not aware and I'm sure

00:10:49.500 --> 00:10:53.060
basically everybody listening
to this have used these two

00:10:53.800 --> 00:10:57.540
technologies probably
