00:39:04.036 --> 00:39:07.266
around basic... as a wrapper to...

00:39:07.336 --> 00:39:09.176
- Well, yes- ... people do.

00:39:09.196 --> 00:39:13.116
People do, right? There was a
lot of problems with mostly,

00:39:13.236 --> 00:39:17.136
Cloud providers who are basically
running some open source tools,

00:39:17.576 --> 00:39:21.476
In the cloud and just give you the API to

