distributions and developers moved back to

02:37:21.248 --> 02:37:24.828
FFmpeg." Yeah, that was a, that was a weird
experience 'cause, you know, I'm a Linux user,

02:37:24.928 --> 02:37:28.878
perspective, that was a weird experience
