02:57:09.664 --> 02:57:13.434
free and open source thing so
that things look good for my, my

02:57:13.524 --> 02:57:17.234
customers and build the best." And to
this day, I personally still try and

02:57:17.264 --> 02:57:20.884
avoid watching the most
cinematic films on streaming

02:57:20.924 --> 02:57:23.844
services and buy the physical
discs because they look,

02:57:24.884 --> 02:57:28.624
they look good without even having to buy an
expensive TV. I think that's the key thing.

02:57:28.884 --> 02:57:32.883
- And x264 is yet another example of
open source project. It was started by

02:57:33.064 --> 02:57:36.704
Laurent Ehrsam when he was at École
Centrale Paris, where VLC was born.

02:57:37.104 --> 02:57:40.984
And then you got a generation of
people like Loren, like Jason, like,

02:57:41.044 --> 02:57:43.644
uh, Måns, like so many-

02:57:43.744 --> 02:57:44.184
- Henrik from-

02:57:44.384 --> 02:57:45.144
- Henrik, uh-

02:57:45.284 --> 02:57:45.554
- Anton, uh

02:57:45.554 --> 02:57:49.244
- ... and this is-- Anton, and
this is where the assembly

02:57:49.324 --> 02:57:53.044
thing that we use now on FFmpeg,
dav1d and so on, was born, right? So

02:57:53.164 --> 02:57:56.934
x264 is, like, amazing project with
people who were really all over the

02:57:57.004 --> 02:57:59.464
world, and I think most of
them never met each other.

02:57:59.984 --> 02:58:03.724
- But all of them, according to
Kieran, or large percentage, love

02:58:03.844 --> 02:58:07.836
anime. There's several things I've
never got into, and one of them

02:58:07.876 --> 02:58:09.026
is anime, and I need to

02:58:09.076 --> 02:58:16.116
- I watch anime so much, especially at
the time. Like, at the time it was like

02:58:17.356 --> 02:58:21.296
a lot of anime content doesn't
exist commercially, right? We

02:58:21.316 --> 02:58:25.076
are before Crunchyroll, right? So
what happens is usually people who

02:58:25.156 --> 02:58:28.756
love anime, who take some
things, some DVDs in

02:58:28.776 --> 02:58:33.636
Japan and rip them because there
is no commercial offering. And-

02:58:33.646 --> 02:58:37.316
... some of the people who are, what
