02:59:14.716 --> 02:59:17.716
textures that you get- ... because
anime is not done in a normal fashion.

02:59:17.796 --> 02:59:21.766
- Yeah. The way you produce it is not--
You, you mostly produce it, like,

02:59:21.796 --> 02:59:25.676
on screens, right? Since a bit of time,
and you have all those gradients,

02:59:26.056 --> 02:59:30.036
right? In colors, because they are very
easy to produce digitally, very complex

02:59:30.076 --> 02:59:33.696
to produce in real life. And the

02:59:33.716 --> 02:59:37.136
subtitles also are very complex
because you need to have often the

02:59:37.216 --> 02:59:40.966
Japanese and then you need to
